#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:65
msgid ":guilabel:`Date`: the batch's creation date."
msgstr ":guilabel:`תאריך`: תאריך יצירת האצווה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reference`: the reference of the batch. Leave it empty to "
