msgstr ":guilabel:`הוסף שורה`: לחץ עליו כדי לבחור את התשלומים שיכללו באצווה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:69
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:83
msgid ""
"Once all desired payments are included, click :guilabel:`Validate` to "
