"תשלום` או :menuselection:`ספקים --> אצוות תשלום`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:89
msgid "All payments in a batch *must* use the same payment method."
msgstr "כל התשלומים באצווה *חייבים* להשתמש באותה שיטת תשלום."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once validated, no additional payments can be added to a batch. You can "
