"מעקב מוגדרות כברירת מחדל."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:23
msgid ""
"To modify a follow-up level, click on the record. From the form view, edit "
"the :guilabel:`Description` or adjust the number of days before a reminder "
