"Accounting <egypt/e-invoicing-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:49
msgid ""
"Access your company profile on the ETA portal by clicking on :guilabel:`View "
"Taxpayer Profile`."
msgstr ""
"גשו לפרופיל החברה שלכם בפורטל ה-ETA על ידי לחיצה על :guilabel:`View Taxpayer "
