#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:None
msgid "Clicking on \"View Taxpayer Profile\" on an ETA invoicing portal"
msgstr "לחיצה על \"View Taxpayer Profile\" בפורטל חשבוניות ETA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:55
msgid ""
"Next, go to the :guilabel:`Representatives` section and then click "
"on :guilabel:`Register ERP`. Fill out the :guilabel:`ERP Name` (e.g., "
"``Odoo``) and leave the other fields empty."
