#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:693
msgid ""
"The journal :guilabel:`type` would be :guilabel:`bank`, because the bank's "
"move percentage (75%) exceeds the threshold (70%)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`סוג` היומן יהיה :guilabel:`בנק`, מכיוון שאחוז התנועות של הבנק "
"(75%) עולה על הסף (70%)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:701
msgid ""
"Each contact keeps its :guilabel:`Reference` from the :guilabel:`CompAuxNum` "
"field."
msgstr "כל איש קשר שומר על :guilabel:`ההפניה` שלו משדה :guilabel:`CompAuxNum`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:704
msgid ""
"These fields are searchable based on previous FEC imports for fiscal/audit "
