"ל-:guilabel:`חקלאות`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:178
msgid ""
"Go to the contact form (:menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Customers` or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors`, for "
"example), and select a contact."
msgstr ""
"עבור לטופס איש הקשר (:menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers` "
"או :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors`, לדוגמה), ובחר באיש "
"קשר."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:180
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, set the :guilabel:`Industry` field "
"to :guilabel:`Agriculture`."
msgstr ""
"בכרטיסייה :guilabel:`מכירות ורכש`, הגדר את השדה :guilabel:`ענף` "
"ל-:guilabel:`חקלאות`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:183
msgid ""
"Repeat this operation for all contacts related to the **agriculture** "
"industry."
msgstr "חזור על פעולה זו עבור כל אנשי הקשר הקשורים לענף ה**חקלאות**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:188
msgid "Veri*Factu"
msgstr "Veri*Factu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:191
msgid ""
"Producers of Veri*Factu billing systems must self-certify their compliance "
"with the regulations. :download:`Download Odoo's \"declaración "
"responsable\"<spain/declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"
msgstr ""
"יצרני מערכות חשבוניות Veri*Factu חייבים לאשר בעצמם את תאימותם "
"לתקנות. :download:`הורד את ה-\"declaración responsable\" של Odoo<spain/"
"declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:194
msgid ""
"**Veri*Factu** is the Spanish Tax Agency's verifiable invoice issuance "
"system. It is mandatory for most taxpayers in Spain, except for those who "
"use the SII system or are under a regional tax regime (i.e., TicketBai)."
msgstr ""
"**Veri*Factu** היא מערכת הנפקת חשבוניות ניתנות לאימות של רשות המסים הספרדית. "
"היא חובה עבור רוב משלמי המסים בספרד, למעט אלה המשתמשים במערכת SII או נמצאים "
"תחת משטר מס אזורי (כלומר, TicketBai)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:198
msgid ""
"Odoo allows :ref:`invoices <localizations/spain/veri-factu-invoices>` and "
"Point of Sale :ref:`orders <localizations/spain/veri-factu-orders>` to be "
"automatically sent to the tax authorities."
msgstr ""
"Odoo umožňuje automatické odesílání :ref:`faktur <localizations/spain/veri-"
"factu-invoices>` a :ref:`objednávek <localizations/spain/veri-factu-orders>` "
"z pokladny daňovým úřadům."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:206
msgid "To enable **Veri\\*Factu**, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pro povolení **Veri\\*Factu** postupujte takto:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:208
msgid ""
"Open the Settings app to make sure your company's :guilabel:`Country` "
"and :guilabel:`Tax ID` are correctly set in the :ref:`Companies <general/"
"companies/company>` section."
msgstr ""
"Otevřete aplikaci Nastavení a ujistěte se, že :guilabel:`Země` "
"a :guilabel:`DIČ` vaší společnosti jsou správně nastaveny v "
"sekci :ref:`Společnosti <general/companies/company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:210
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Spain - Veri*Factu` "
"(`l10n_es_edi_verifactu`) module."
msgstr ""
":ref:`התקן <general/install>` את המודול :guilabel:`Spain - Veri*Factu` "
"(`l10n_es_edi_verifactu`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:212
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` "
"or :menuselection:`Invoicing --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section, check the :guilabel:`Enable "
"Veri*Factu` option, and click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage "
"certificates` to add a certificate."
msgstr ""
"עבור אל :menuselection:`חשבונאות --> תצורה --> הגדרות` "
"או :menuselection:`חשבוניות --> תצורה --> הגדרות`, גלול למטה "
"לקטע :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu`, סמן את האפשרות :guilabel:`הפעל Veri*Factu`, "
"ולחץ על :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`ניהול אישורים` כדי להוסיף אישור."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:216
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Certificates for Veri\\*Factu` list view, "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"V zobrazení seznamu :guilabel:`Certificates for Veri\\*Factu` klikněte "
"na :guilabel:`Nový`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:217
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Upload your file`, then select a certificate file and enter "
"the :guilabel:`Password` needed to open the certificate (if there is one)."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Upload your file`, poté vyberte soubor certifikátu a "
"zadejte :guilabel:`Heslo` potřebné k otevření certifikátu (pokud existuje)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:221
msgid "At least one certificate has to be uploaded."
msgstr "Musí být nahrán alespoň jeden certifikát."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:222
msgid ""
"By default, Veri*Factu is in testing mode. The data is sent to test servers "
"and is not considered official. When official data can be sent to the "
"production servers, go to the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section in "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` and disable :guilabel:`Test Environment`."
msgstr ""
"כברירת מחדל, Veri*Factu נמצא במצב בדיקה. הנתונים נשלחים לשרתי בדיקה ואינם "
"נחשבים רשמיים. כאשר ניתן לשלוח נתונים רשמיים לשרתי הייצור, עבור "
"לקטע :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` ב:guilabel:`הגדרות` והשבת את :guilabel:`סביבת "
"בדיקה`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:232
msgid ""
"Once an :doc:`invoice <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` is "
"confirmed, it can be :ref:`sent <accounting/invoice/sending>`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Send` window, the Veri*Factu option is available if "
"Veri*Factu has been enabled."
msgstr ""
"Jakmile je :doc:`faktura <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices>` "
"potvrzena, může být :ref:`odeslána <accounting/invoice/sending>`. V "
"okně :guilabel:`Odeslat` je k dispozici možnost Veri*Factu, pokud byla "
"povolena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:236
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to generate a JSON file containing the invoice "
"details. This file is stored as a Veri*Factu document. In "
"the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` tab, all corresponding documents are listed by "
"their creation date and current status."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Odeslat` pro vygenerování souboru JSON obsahujícího "
"podrobnosti faktury. Tento soubor je uložen jako dokument Veri*Factu. Na "
"kartě :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` jsou uvedeny všechny odpovídající dokumenty "
"podle data vytvoření a aktuálního stavu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:241
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:266
msgid ""
"To download a JSON file, click on its document in the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` "
"tab. Then, in the :guilabel:`Open: Veri*Factu Documents` window, click the "
"link in the :guilabel:`JSON` field."
msgstr ""
"Pro stažení souboru JSON klikněte na jeho dokument na "
"kartě :guilabel:`Veri*Factu`. Poté v okně :guilabel:`Open: Veri*Factu "
"Documents` klikněte na odkaz v poli :guilabel:`JSON`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:245
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:270
msgid ""
"The document should be sent to the :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)` immediately. However, it may be delayed due to "
"mandatory waiting periods between submissions required by the :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`. In such cases, the document "
"is automatically sent the next time a scheduled action runs."
msgstr ""
"Dokument by měl být odeslán :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de Administración "
"Tributaria)` okamžitě. Může však dojít ke zpoždění kvůli povinnému čekacímu "
"období mezi odesláními vyžadovanému :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)`. V takových případech je dokument automaticky "
"odeslán při příštím spuštění plánované akce."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:249
msgid ""
"A Veri\\*Factu **QR code** appears on the invoice PDF. Scan this code to "
"verify that the invoice has been received and recognized by the :abbr:`AEAT "
"(Agencia Estatal de Administración Tributaria)`."
msgstr ""
"Na PDF faktuře se zobrazí **QR kód** Veri\\*Factu. Naskenujte tento kód pro "
"ověření, že faktura byla přijata a rozpoznána :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal "
"de Administración Tributaria)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:256
msgid "Point of sale orders"
msgstr "Objednávky z pokladny"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:258
msgid ""
"Once an order has been :ref:`paid <pos/sell>`, a JSON file containing the "
"order details is generated. This file is stored as a Veri*Factu document."
msgstr ""
"Jakmile je objednávka :ref:`zaplacena <pos/sell>`, vygeneruje se soubor JSON "
"obsahující údaje o objednávce. Tento soubor je uložen jako dokument "
"Veri*Factu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:261
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Orders` list view, select the relevant order. In "
"the :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` tab, all the corresponding documents are listed "
"by their creation date and current status."
msgstr ""
"Přejděte na :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`. V "
"zobrazení seznamu :guilabel:`Objednávky` vyberte příslušnou objednávku. Na "
"kartě :guilabel:`Veri*Factu` jsou uvedeny všechny odpovídající dokumenty "
"podle data vytvoření a aktuálního stavu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:275
msgid ""
"If an invoice is generated for an order during the payment process, the "
"Veri*Factu document is :ref:`created and sent for the invoice <localizations/"
"spain/veri-factu-invoices>` instead."
msgstr ""
"Pokud je pro objednávku během procesu platby vygenerována faktura, dokument "
"Veri*Factu je :ref:`vytvořen a odeslán pro fakturu <localizations/spain/veri-"
"factu-invoices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:279
msgid ""
"A Veri\\*Factu **QR code** appears on the order receipt, even if an invoice "
"is created for the order. Scan this code to verify that the invoice has been "
"received and recognized by the :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de "
"Administración Tributaria)`"
msgstr ""
"Na účtence objednávky se zobrazí **QR kód** Veri\\*Factu, i když je pro "
"objednávku vytvořena faktura. Naskenujte tento kód pro ověření, že faktura "
"byla přijata a rozpoznána :abbr:`AEAT (Agencia Estatal de Administración "
"Tributaria)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:286
msgid "TicketBAI"
msgstr "TicketBAI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:288
msgid ""
"`Ticket BAI <https://www.gipuzkoa.eus/es/web/ogasuna/ticketbai>`_ or "
"**TBAI** is an e-Invoicing system used by the Basque government and its "
"three provincial councils (Álava, Biscay, and Gipuzkoa). Odoo supports the "
"**TicketBAI (TBAI)** electronic invoicing format for all three regions of "
"the **Basque Country**."
msgstr ""
"`Ticket BAI <https://www.gipuzkoa.eus/es/web/ogasuna/ticketbai>`_ או "
"**TBAI** היא מערכת חשבוניות אלקטרוניות המשמשת את ממשלת חבל הבאסקים ושלוש "
"המועצות המחוזיות שלה (אלבה, ביסקאיה וגיפוסקואה). Odoo תומך בפורמט חשבוניות "
"אלקטרוניות **TicketBAI (TBAI)** עבור כל שלושת האזורים של **חבל הבאסקים**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:294
msgid "To use TicketBAI, make sure:"
msgstr "כדי להשתמש ב-TicketBAI, ודא ש:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:296
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Country` and :guilabel:`Tax ID` fields on the :doc:`company "
"record <../../general/companies>` are filled in."
msgstr ""
"השדות :guilabel:`מדינה` ו-:guilabel:`מזהה מס` ב:doc:`רשומת החברה <../../"
"general/companies>` מלאים."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:298
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Spain -TicketBAI` (`l10n_es_edi_TBAI`) module is :ref:`installed "
"<general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"המודול :guilabel:`ספרד - TicketBAI` (`l10n_es_edi_TBAI`) :ref:`מותקן "
"<general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:300
msgid "To configure TicketBAI, follow these steps:"
msgstr "כדי להגדיר את TicketBAI, בצע שלבים אלה:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:302
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"down to the :guilabel:`Spain Localization` section."
msgstr ""
"עבור אל :menuselection:`חשבונאות --> תצורה --> הגדרות` וגלול למטה אל "
"הקטע :guilabel:`לוקליזציה ספרדית`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:304
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Registro de Libros connection TicketBAI` section, select a "
"region in the :guilabel:`Tax Agency for TBAI` field and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"בקטע :guilabel:`חיבור Registro de Libros TicketBAI`, בחר אזור "
"בשדה :guilabel:`רשות המס עבור TBAI` ו:guilabel:`שמור`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:306
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Manage certificates (TicketBAI)`."
msgstr "לחץ על :guilabel:`ניהול אישורים (TicketBAI)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:307
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Certificates for EDI TicketBAI invoices on Spain` view, "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"בתצוגת :guilabel:`אישורים עבור חשבוניות EDI TicketBAI בספרד`, לחץ "
"על :guilabel:`חדש`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:308
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Upload your file` to upload the certificate, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Certificate Password` provided by the tax agency, and "
"select :guilabel:`TBAI` in the :guilabel:`Certificate scope` field."
msgstr ""
"לחץ על :guilabel:`העלה את הקובץ שלך` כדי להעלות את האישור, הזן "
"את :guilabel:`סיסמת האישור` שסופקה על ידי רשות המס ובחר :guilabel:`TBAI` "
"בשדה :guilabel:`היקף האישור`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:313
msgid ""
"To test certificates, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` and, in the :guilabel:`Spain Localization` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`TBAI Test Mode`."
msgstr ""
"כדי לבדוק אישורים, עבור אל :menuselection:`חשבונאות --> תצורה --> הגדרות` "
"ובקטע :guilabel:`לוקליזציה ספרדית`, הפעל :guilabel:`מצב בדיקה TBAI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:319
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:361
msgid "Use case"
msgstr "מקרה שימוש"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:321
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:363
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is :ref:`created <accounting/invoice/creation>` "
"and :ref:`confirmed <accounting/invoice/confirmation>`, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"לאחר ש:ref:`נוצרה <accounting/invoice/creation>` ו:ref:`אושרה <accounting/"
"invoice/confirmation>` חשבונית, בצע שלבים אלה:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:325
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Print & Send` window, make sure the :guilabel:`TicketBAI` "
"option is enabled and click :guilabel:`Send`"
msgstr ""
"בחלון :guilabel:`הדפס ושלח`, ודא שהאפשרות :guilabel:`TicketBAI` מופעלת ולחץ "
"על :guilabel:`שלח`"

