#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/mercado_pago.rst:34
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab, fill in the :guilabel:`Access Token` "
"with the value you saved at the :ref:`payment_providers/mercado_pago/"
