"<payment_providers/test-mode>` ו:ref:`מפתחות API <payment_providers/stripe/"
"stripe-configuration>` של `מצב הבדיקה של חשבון Stripe שלך או סביבת ארגז חול "
"<https://docs.stripe.com/testing-use-cases>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:91
msgid ""
"To link the same Stripe account to :doc:`multiple companies </applications/"
"general/companies/multi_company>` in a database, :ref:`create an account "
"<payment_providers/stripe/create_account>` and :ref:`fill in the credentials "
"<payment_providers/stripe/manual_input>` for one company, then reuse the "
"same credentials and webhook for the others. To view the webhook, go to the "
"`Webhooks page on Stripe <https://dashboard.stripe.com/webhooks>`_, or log "
"into your Stripe dashboard and go to :menuselection:`Developers --> "
"Webhooks`. Click the destination in the list, then click the :icon:`fa-eye` "
"(:guilabel:`Reveal secret`) icon next to the :guilabel:`Signing secret` "
"field and copy the value."
msgstr ""
"כדי לקשר את אותו חשבון Stripe ל:doc:`מספר חברות </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` במסד נתונים, :ref:`צור חשבון <payment_providers/"
"stripe/create_account>` ו:ref:`מלא את פרטי הגישה <payment_providers/stripe/"
"manual_input>` עבור חברה אחת, ולאחר מכן השתמש שוב באותם פרטי גישה ו-webhook "
"עבור החברות האחרות. כדי להציג את ה-webhook, עבור ל`דף ה-Webhooks ב-Stripe "
"<https://dashboard.stripe.com/webhooks>`_, או היכנס ללוח הבקרה של Stripe שלך "
"ועבור אל :menuselection:`Developers --> Webhooks`. לחץ על היעד ברשימה, ולאחר "
"מכן לחץ על :icon:`fa-eye` (:guilabel:`Reveal secret`) ליד "
"השדה :guilabel:`Signing secret` והעתק את הערך."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:102
msgid "Enable Apple Pay"
msgstr "הפעלת Apple Pay"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:104
msgid ""
"To allow customers to use the Apple Pay button to pay for their eCommerce "
"orders, :ref:`navigate to the Stripe payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`, then go to the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab, "
"enable :guilabel:`Allow Express Checkout`, and click :guilabel:`Enable Apple "
"Pay`."
msgstr ""
"כדי לאפשר ללקוחות להשתמש בכפתור Apple Pay לתשלום עבור הזמנות המסחר האלקטרוני "
"שלהם, :ref:`נווט לספק התשלום Stripe <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`, ולאחר מכן עבור לכרטיסייה :guilabel:`Configuration`, "
"הפעל :guilabel:`Allow Express Checkout`, ולחץ :guilabel:`Enable Apple Pay`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:110
msgid ""
":ref:`Express checkout and Google Pay <payment_providers/express_checkout>`"
msgstr ":ref:`תשלום מהיר ו-Google Pay <payment_providers/express_checkout>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/stripe.rst:113
msgid ""
"Stripe allows to :ref:`manually capture <payment_providers/manual_capture>` "
"and :ref:`refund <payment_providers/refunds>` payments either from Odoo or "
"directly from the Stripe dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Stripe מאפשר :ref:`ללכוד ידנית <payment_providers/manual_capture>` "
"ו:ref:`להחזיר <payment_providers/refunds>` תשלומים מ-Odoo או ישירות מלוח "
"הבקרה של Stripe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:3
msgid "Wire transfers"
msgstr "העברות בנקאיות"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **Wire Transfer** payment method allows you to provide payment "
"instructions to your customers, such as your bank details and a reference to "
"include with the payment. These instructions are displayed after the "
"customer selects :guilabel:`Wire Transfer` as the payment method and clicks "
"the :guilabel:`Pay now` button at the end of the checkout process on your "
"ecommerce website or on the customer portal."
msgstr ""
"Platební metoda **Bankovní převod** umožňuje poskytnout vašim zákazníkům "
"platební instrukce, jako jsou vaše bankovní údaje a reference, kterou mají "
"uvést s platbou. Tyto instrukce se zobrazí poté, co zákazník "
"vybere :guilabel:`Wire Transfer` jako platební metodu a klikne na "
"tlačítko :guilabel:`Pay now` na konci procesu objednávky na vašem e-shopu "
"nebo v zákaznickém portálu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:None
msgid "Payment instructions on the customer portal"
msgstr "הוראות תשלום בפורטל הלקוח"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:16
msgid ""
"While this method is widely accessible and requires minimal setup, it is not "
"efficient process-wise. It is recommended to set up a :doc:`payment provider "
"<../payment_providers>` instead."
msgstr ""
"אמנם שיטה זו נגישה באופן נרחב ודורשת הגדרה מינימלית, אך היא אינה יעילה "
"מבחינת התהליך. מומלץ להגדיר :doc:`payment provider <../payment_providers>` "
"במקום זאת."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:19
msgid ""
"Online orders remain in the :guilabel:`Quotation sent` (i.e., unpaid order) "
"stage until you receive the payment and manually :guilabel:`Confirm` the "
"order."
msgstr ""
"הזמנות מקוונות נשארות בשלב :guilabel:`Quotation sent` (כלומר, הזמנה שלא "
"שולמה) עד שתקבל את התשלום ו:guilabel:`Confirm` באופן ידני את ההזמנה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Wire transfer** can be used as a template for other payment methods that "
"are processed manually, such as checks, by renaming or duplicating it."
msgstr ""
"**העברה בנקאית** ניתנת לשימוש כתבנית לשיטות תשלום אחרות המעובדות באופן ידני, "
"כגון צ'קים, על ידי שינוי שם או שכפול שלה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:29
msgid "To configure **Wire Transfer**:"
msgstr "Pro nastavení **bankovního převodu**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:31
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the Wire Transfer payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Navigate to the Wire Transfer payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:38
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Enable QR codes` to activate QR code payments."
msgstr "הפעל :guilabel:`Enable QR codes` כדי להפעיל תשלומי קוד QR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:44
msgid ""
"Define the payment instructions in the :guilabel:`Messages` tab. If :doc:`a "
"bank account <../accounting/bank>` has already been defined, the account "
"number is automatically added to the default message generated by Odoo. You "
"can also add it afterward and update the message by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Reload pending message`."
msgstr ""
"הגדר את הוראות התשלום בלשונית :guilabel:`Messages`. אם :doc:`a bank account "
"<../accounting/bank>` כבר הוגדר, מספר החשבון מתוסף אוטומטית להודעת ברירת "
"המחדל שנוצרה על ידי Odoo. אתה יכול גם להוסיף אותו לאחר מכן ולעדכן את ההודעה "
"על ידי לחיצה על :guilabel:`Reload pending message`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:0
msgid "Define payment instructions"
msgstr "הגדר הוראות תשלום"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:55
msgid ""
"You can also test wire transfers using the :ref:`payment_providers/test-"
"mode`."
msgstr ""
"Bankovní převody můžete také testovat pomocí :ref:`payment_providers/test-"
"mode`."

