msgstr ""
"היכנס ל-`פורטל הסוחר של Worldline <https://merchant-portal.worldline-"
"solutions.com/>`_, לחץ על הסמל :icon:`fa-th` (תפריט :guilabel:`menu`) "
"ובחר :guilabel:`Back Office`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:24
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` and click on :guilabel:`New "
