"של Odoo שלך ואחריה `/payment/worldline/webhook` בשדה :guilabel:`Endpoint "
"url`, ולחץ על :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
msgid "For example: `https://example.odoo.com/payment/worldline/webhook`."
msgstr "לדוגמה: `https://example.odoo.com/payment/worldline/webhook`."

